  Countless legends surround a sword known as Soul Edge.  Some claim it
  was the ultimate weapon.  Others refer to it as the &quot;Sword of Heroes.&quot;
  ...A phantom sword with immeasurable power of the spirits...  the key to
  eternal youth...  treasure without equal...  a panacea to cure all
  illness...  There are even those who consider it the &quot;Sword of
  Salvation.&quot; Now you must enter into a deadly combat tournament and if
  you win, you will lay claim to the Soul Edge! Are you good enough to
  win?
